data.text:
Chicago: Shasta, 1953. Very Fine / Very Fine. Item #002785E

A very fine, crisp, clean and tight copy in a very fine jacket/brodart covered. Stated First Edition. SIGNED BY THE AUTHOR on the front free endpaper. A very nice copy.

Very mild bump to lower right corner of front corner board. Still remains sharp. No tears no chips to jacket. (See Pict's).
